    "#Splitting the data\n",
    "x_train,x_test,y_train,y_test = train_test_split(x,y,random_state = 42, test_size = 0.10)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",

   "source": [
    "# Initialising the CNN\n",
    "model = Sequential()\n",
    "\n",
    "#First Convulation Layer\n",
    "model.add(Conv2D(16,(3,3),activation='relu',input_shape = x_train[0].shape ))\n",
    "model.add(BatchNormalization())\n",
    "#Pooling\n",
    "model.add(MaxPool2D(2,2))\n",
    "model.add(Dropout(0.25))\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "#Second Convulation Layer\n",
    "model.add(Conv2D(32,(3,3),activation='relu',input_shape = x_train[0].shape ))\n",
    "model.add(BatchNormalization())\n",
    "#Pooling\n",
    "model.add(MaxPool2D(2,2))\n",
    "model.add(Dropout(0.25))\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "#Third Convulation Layer\n",
    "model.add(Conv2D(64,(3,3),activation='relu',input_shape = x_train[0].shape ))\n",
    "model.add(BatchNormalization())\n",
    "#Pooling\n",
    "model.add(MaxPool2D(2,2))\n",
    "model.add(Dropout(0.25))\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "#Fourth Convulation Layer\n",
    "model.add(Conv2D(128,(3,3),activation='relu',input_shape = x_train[0].shape ))\n",
    "model.add(BatchNormalization())\n",
    "#Pooling\n",
    "model.add(MaxPool2D(2,2))\n",
    "model.add(Dropout(0.25))\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "#Flattening Layer\n",
    "model.add(Flatten())\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "#First full connection Layer\n",
    "model.add(Dense(128,activation='relu'))\n",
    "model.add(BatchNormalization())\n",
    "model.add(Dropout(0.5))\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "#Second full connection Layer\n",
    "model.add(Dense(128,activation='relu'))\n",
    "model.add(BatchNormalization())\n",
    "model.add(Dropout(0.5))\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "#Output Layer\n",
    "model.add(Dense(25,activation='sigmoid'))"
   ]
  },

   "source": [
    " def plot_learningCurve(history,epoch):\n",
    "   epoch_range = range(1,epoch+1)\n",
    "   plt.plot(epoch_range,history.history['accuracy'])\n",
    "   plt.plot(epoch_range,history.history['val_accuracy'])\n",
    "   plt.title('Model_Accuracy')\n",
    "   plt.ylabel('Accuracy')\n",
    "   plt.xlabel('Epoch')\n",
    "   plt.legend(['Train','Val'],loc = 'upper left')\n",
    "   plt.show()\n",
    "\n",
    "   epoch_range = range(1,epoch+1)\n",
    "   plt.plot(epoch_range,history.history['loss'])\n",
    "   plt.plot(epoch_range,history.history['val_loss'])\n",
    "   plt.title('Model_loss')\n",
    "   plt.ylabel('Loss')\n",
    "   plt.xlabel('Epoch')\n",
    "   plt.legend(['Train','Val'],loc = 'upper left')\n",
    "   plt.show()"
   ]
